OL,3,CPrisoners to be released two months
OL,4,Cearly to help ease overcrowding in
OL,5,Cjails
OL,7,FPrisoners will be released up to two
OL,8,Fmonths early to help overcrowding in
OL,9,Fprisons, the justice secretary has
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FAlex Chalk announced a plan to extend
OL,13,Fa scheme which allows "certain low-
OL,14,Flevel offenders" to be released from
OL,15,Fprison early because prisons are
OL,16,Fnearing capacity.
OL,18,FPreviously prisoners could be released
OL,19,Fup to 18 days before the end of the
OL,20,Fsentence, but this has now been
OL,21,Fincreased to 35-60 days.
