OL,4,Cearly to help ease overcrowding in
OL,5,Cjails
OL,7,FMr Chalk told the Commons the
OL,8,Fgovernment will enable the scheme to
OL,9,Fhappen for "a time limited period",
OL,10,Fand "work with the police, prisons and
OL,11,Fprobation leaders to make further
OL,12,Fadjustments as required".
OL,14,FITV News Political Correspondent Carl
OL,15,FDinnen discusses how much earlier
OL,16,Fprisoners could now be released
OL,18,FMr Chalk also said electronic tags
OL,19,Fwill be used to "enhance public
OL,20,Fprotection" where necessary.
