OL,7,FLabour's Shadow Justice Secretary
OL,8,FShabana Mahmood said this policy is
OL,9,F"the most drastic form of early
OL,10,Frelease for prisoners that this
OL,11,Fcountry has ever seen".
OL,13,F"This is a measure that will cause
OL,14,Fshockwaves and deep concern across our
OL,15,Fcountry", she said.
