OL,7,FMs Mahmood said in Mr Chalk's eleven
OL,8,Fpage statement on early release
OL,9,F"merited one paragraph", and accused
OL,10,Fthe government of "trying to quietly
OL,11,Fslip out" the policy by releasing a
OL,12,Fstatement late on Monday evening.
OL,14,FMale prisons are 99.7 per cent full,
OL,15,Fwith just 238 spaces left according to
OL,16,Fthe Daily Telegraph, while women's
OL,17,Fjails are 96.9 per cent full with just
OL,18,F118 spaces left.
