OL,7,FMr Chalk had previously announced in
OL,8,FOctober that the government will use
OL,9,Fits powers to allow the prison service
OL,10,Fto let some prisoners out of jail up
OL,11,Fto 18 days early, but this did not
OL,12,Fapply to "anyone serving a life
OL,13,Fsentence, anyone serving an extended
OL,14,Fdeterminate sentence, anyone serving a
OL,15,Fsentence for an offence of particular
OL,16,Fconcern, anyone convicted of a serious
OL,17,Fviolence offence, anyone convicted of
OL,18,Fterrorism, (and) anyone convicted of a
OL,19,Fsex offence."
