OL,7,FThe scheme is called the end of
OL,8,Fcustody supervised license (ECSL)
OL,9,Fscheme.
OL,11,FAsked whether this new early release
OL,12,Fscheme could become a permanent
OL,13,Fsituation, the prime minister's
OL,14,Fofficial spokesman, said: "No, it is a
OL,15,Ftemporary measure and it will be used
OL,16,Fat an operational level by the Prison
OL,17,Fand Probation Service.
OL,19,F"They won't be in place any longer
OL,20,Fthan is absolutely necessary."
