OL,7,FIn a statement released late on Monday
OL,8,Fevening, Mr Chalk said there was a
OL,9,Fneed to "address the unsustainable
OL,10,Fgrowth in the remand population" since
OL,11,Fthe coronavirus pandemic, saying those
OL,12,Fheld in remand had increased by more
OL,13,Fthan 6,000 in 2019 to more than 16,000
OL,14,Fat present.
OL,16,FMr Chalk said, as well as extending
OL,17,Fthe ability for prison governors to
OL,18,Frelease prisoners early, the UK
OL,19,Fgovernment would be increasing support
OL,20,Ffor bail applications.
