OL,7,FIn his statement on Monday, he said
OL,8,Fministers were "exploring at pace with
OL,9,Fthe senior judiciary the rollout of a
OL,10,Fremote, nationwide, pilot, crown court
OL,11,Fcapable of hearing new bail
OL,12,Fapplications".
OL,14,FHe added: "The pilot would monitor
OL,15,Fwhether these additional measures
OL,16,Fresult in an increase in the use of
OL,17,Ftagging and appropriate support
OL,18,Fpackages in bail applications.
