OL,7,F"In order to support this, the
OL,8,FGovernment will invest #53 million
OL,9,Fadditional funding to expand the Bail
OL,10,FInformation Service ` part of the
OL,11,Fproductivity package the Chancellor
OL,12,Fannounced at the Budget.
OL,14,F"This will enable our court system to
OL,15,Fbe more efficient by increasing the
OL,16,Fcourt-based staff and digital systems
OL,17,Fthat can provide critical information
OL,18,Fto the judiciary ` making the bail
OL,19,Fprocess more efficient.
